                  "PHOTO"
                ],
                "reaction": null
              },
              "free_text": [
                " The photo-neutron target was composed of ten",
                "Ta plates with a diameter of 4.9 cm and an effective",
                "thickness of 7.4 cm. There was a 0.15 cm water gap",
                "between Ta plates in order to cool the target",
                "effectively. The housing of the target was made of",
                "titanium."
              ]
            }
          ],
          "SAMPLE": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": null,
              "free_text": [
                "A high-purity (>99.99%) Mo foil with a natural isotopic",
                "composition (92Mo 14.84%, 94Mo 9.25%, 95Mo 15.92%,",
                "96Mo 16.68%, 97Mo 9.55%, 98Mo 24.13%, and 100Mo 9.63%)",
                "was used for measuring the thermal neutron cross-sect.",
                "and the resonance integral of the 98Mo(n,gamma)99Mo",
                "reaction.",
                "Natural Mo metallic foils were 12.7 mm in diameter and",
                "0.1 mm in thickness. The Au and In metallic foils were",
                "used as the comparator reactions and the neutron flux",
                "monitors, respectively.",
                "      Characteristics of Mo, Au and In foils:",
                " Foil Diam.(mm) Thick.(mm)  Weight (g)       Purity (%)",
                " Au 1  12.7       0.03    0.0731+-0.0004      99.95",
                " Au 2  12.7       0.03    0.0726+-0.0004      99.95",
                " Mo 2  12.7       0.10    0.1284+-0.0006      99.90",
                " Mo 3  12.7       0.10    0.1290+-0.0006      99.90",
                " In 11 12.7       0.05    0.0470+-0.0004      99.99",
                " In 12 12.7       0.05    0.0466+-0.0004      99.99",
                " In 13 12.7       0.05    0.0471+-0.0004      99.99",
                " In 14 12.7       0.05    0.0468+-0.0004      99.99",
                " In 15 12.7       0.05    0.0472+-0.0004      99.99",
                " In 16 12.7       0.05    0.0471+-0.0004      99.99"
              ]
            }
